Thursday, June 18, 1992

MERIT DOCKET

90-2332. State ex rel. Hadlock v. Bonanno.

In Mandamus. On response to show cause order and on motion for summary judgment. Sua sponte, cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Douglas, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur. Holmes and Wright, JJ., would grant the motion for summary judgment.
